commit_message:
Venn: Created a sub-directory for all Venn analysis utility scripts

splitSymbolsVenn.py: A new script to generate feature lists in Venn analysis

Added template Makefile for Venn analysis

Signed-off-by: CharlesJB <Charles.Joly-Beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca>

VennMultiWay.R: Corrected script name in usage

Signed-off-by: CharlesJB <Charles.Joly-Beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca>

GenerateVennInput.py: Will now longer print path to file in header name

Signed-off-by: CharlesJB <Charles.Joly-Beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca>

VennMultiWay.R: A new script to generate a Venn diagram (will work with up to 5 samples)

Signed-off-by: CharlesJB <Charles.Joly-Beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca>

GenerateVennInput.py: New file that convert multiple list of IDs to limma input file with header

Added a README file

First version of ChIP-Seq analysis pipeline implemented with Make.

Signed-off-by: CharlesJB <Charles.Joly-Beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca>

Removing every scripts as they will be replaced by a very different approach

The old scripts will available in the branch named "deprecated".

The new approach will use Makefiles the make the pipeline more robust and reproducible.

Signed-off-by: CharlesJB <Charles.Joly-Beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca>
